name: [AA] Honor Guard Corps
description:
Alpha Authority Honor Guard; A group of warriors who act as the royal guard to the Overlord himself. They are highly trained in VIP protection and crowd management, but are also great defenders and can be deployed to reliably defend our lands while other forces are busy invading.
